      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Uber Sri Lanka today donated US$ 200,000 to the Sri Lanka Red Cross Society to help the vulnerable communities affected by the economic crisis. The donation will be utilised to distribute food and life-saving medicines across the country. Pix by Pradeep Dilrukshana"
